name: Operative on the reinforcing cutting line has uploaded clear photo of open stock bundle boar
Cut and bent bars checked off against detail sheet
Perimeter bars and spacing marks confirmed
Cast in Items checked and marked on cage (Dross Ducts, Inserts Weld Plates)
Overall cage dimensions in plan checked and there will be sufficient concrete cover to edges
Overall cage thickness checked and there will be sufficient cover to MF and TF
There is sufficient cover to rebates around openings or along edge forms
Weld plates can be fitted to cage in correct locations?
Reinforcing details checked/highlighted off against shop drawing (upload photo)
MF Weld plates in correct location and siliconed to table
Panel correctly labeled (check against shop drawing)
Grout holes for Drossbach Ducts have been drilled (top and bottom)
Bottom of Drossbach Duct is clear (any slurry/grout has been removed)
All lifters have been cleared/cleaned out (including top lifters for install)
All Inserts have been exposed and nail plates removed (caps that came with Ancon fixings should be put back on)
Stitch joints have been jet washed
NF chamfers and square edges rounded with cup stone
Weld plates cleaned (NF weld plates to be cleaned with cup stone)
Grade 300 starters bent up for transport (only bend starter down if transport height is increased by bending up)
Structural repairs required (if yes photograph before)
Photo take of Panel on Truck
No remedial work required on site
Test Results, Certificates and Documentation (Reo & Yard QA)
Upload Photo of Reinforcing Stock Bundle Tags (Cast # Tracking)
